  "Clear EEPROM": {
   "width": 12180,
   "height": 8340,
   "color": "rgb(255,255,225)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "Clear EEPROM after replacing TCU or CVT assembly",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 1800,
      "top": 156,
      "height": 552,
      "width": 8520
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@?? ??",
      "size": 16.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "If TCU is replaced with used unit or CVT assembly is replaced with new or used unit, Follow the instructions below for EEPROM clear.",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 840,
      "top": 840,
      "height": 600,
      "width": 10560
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@?? ??",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": " 1. Turn the ignition swich \"ON\"",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 1200,
      "top": 1476,
      "height": 420,
      "width": 9960
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@?? ??",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": " 4. Rlease brake pedal and accelerator pedal",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 1200,
      "top": 5880,
      "height": 420,
      "width": 7560
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@?? ??",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": " 3. Click \"EEPROM Clear\" button while depressing the brake pedal with the left foot and the accelerator        pedal slightly with the right foot (accelerator pedal angle : approximately 2/8)",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,255)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 1200,
      "top": 2100,
      "height": 660,
      "width": 10440
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@?? ??",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": " 2. Shift the selector lever to \"R\" position",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 1200,
      "top": 1788,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 7560
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@?? ??",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": " 5. Turn the ignition switch \"OFF\" and hold it for 10 seconds or more while keeping the selector lever     in \"R\" position",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 1200,
      "top": 6240,
      "height": 612,
      "width": 10080
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@?? ??",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": " 6. Turn the ignition switch \"ON\" while keeping the selector lever in \"R\" position",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 1200,
      "top": 6864,
      "height": 420,
      "width": 9600
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@?? ??",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": " 7. Set the selector lever to \"P\" position and Check that the shift position in combination meter turns ON",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 1200,
      "top": 7224,
      "height": 480,
      "width": 10560
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@?? ??",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "    Then you can see that 6 monitoring values in the list below are immediately changed to \"0\"",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 1200,
      "top": 2664,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 10320
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@?? ??",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "    Now you can see that the above 6 data are changed to new values",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 1200,
      "top": 7536,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 8280
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@?? ??",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    }
   ],
   "presend": [
    {
     "Delay": "10",
     "RequestName": "ClearDTC"
    }
   ],
